);font-family:Georgia,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,Times,serif">Defense foreca=
sting, or predicting the future operational environment, is used in DoD&#39=
;s planning, programming, budgeting, and execution system (PPBES), and is, =
&quot;generally static, linear, and reasonably mechanical&quot; in its appr=
